thread.title: India’s SpiceJet Could Order Up to 250 Aircraft by End of March
thread.title_full: India’s SpiceJet Could Order Up to 250 Aircraft by End of March - WSJ

author: Santanu Choudhury
title: India’s SpiceJet Could Order Up to 250 Aircraft by End of March
text:
NEW DELHI—Indian low-cost carrier SpiceJet Ltd. is making money again and plans to order new aircraft worth billions of dollars in the next five months, said its chairman.
As the once-struggling airline gets set for a new round of expansion, it could order more than 200 aircraft by the end of March.
It is in advance stages of discussions...
